query:
SELECT v.id as v_id, v.formandoId, f.turmaId, v.excluido,
       DATE_FORMAT(v.dataVenda, '%d/%m/%Y %H:%i:%s') as data_formatada
FROM vendas v 
INNER JOIN formandos f ON v.formandoId = f.id
WHERE v.dataVenda BETWEEN '2026-06-14 00:00:00' AND '2026-06-15 23:59:59'
  AND v.excluido = 0
  AND f.turmaId IS NULL
